title: Time.Team.-.2000.-.Complete.Series.-.13.episodes
description:
Complete Time Team Series 7 from 2000.

Originally downloaded from Mininova, thanks go to the original Upper and Capper! :-D

Episodes: (Courtesy Wikipedia)

  1. 2 January 2000 - Denia, Spain: Muslim port.
  2. 9 January 2000 - Cirencester, Gloucestershire: Roman town and temple.
  3. 16 January 2000 - Wierre Effroy, France: Spitfire crash site.
  4. 23 January 2000 - Waddon, Dorset: Iron-Age site.
  5. 30 January 2000 - Birdoswald, Cumbria: Roman fort beside Hadrian&#039;s Wall.
  6. 6 February 2000 - Elveden, Suffolk: Stone-Age settlement.
  7. 13 February 2000 - Coventry, West Midlands: Medieval cathedral.
  8. 20 February 2000 - Basing House, Hampshire: Tudor building.
  9. 27 February 2000 - Flag Fen, Cambridgeshire: Bronze-Age trackway.
 10. 5 March 2000 - Sutton St Michael, Herefordshire: Saxon site, possibly Offa&#039;s palace.
 11. 12 March 2000 - Greenwich, London: Roman site.
 12. 19 March 2000 - Hartlepool, Durham: Anglo-saxon monastery.
 13. 26 March 2000 - York, Yorkshire: Roman cemetery, Viking buildings and the medieval St Leonard&#039;s hospital (highlights from the 1999 live broadcasts).
